# Kafka Connect — connectors with status, then the connector detail tabs
Output vhs/gifs/kafka-connect.gif
Source vhs/_config.tape

Hide
Type "./kafui --mock --resource connectors" Enter
Sleep 3s
Show

Sleep 2500ms
Down@400ms 2
Sleep 1s
# Open connector detail
Enter
Sleep 2500ms
# Cycle Overview / Tasks / Config / Topics tabs
Tab
Sleep 1800ms
Tab
Sleep 1800ms
Tab
Sleep 1500ms
Escape
Sleep 1200ms

Hide
Ctrl+C
